<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Chinese_character&amp;action=edit&amp;section=46" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<table class="metadata plainlinks mbox-small" style="border:1px solid #aaa; background-color:#f9f9f9;">
<tr>
<td class="mbox-image"><a href="http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:Search/Chinese_character" title="commons:Special:Search/Chinese character"><img alt="Sister project" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4a/Commons-logo.svg/40px-Commons-logo.svg.png" width="40" height="54" border="0" /></a></td>
<td class="mbox-text" style=""><a href="/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons" title="Wikimedia Commons">Wikimedia Commons</a> has media related to: <i><b><a href="http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Chinese_Characters" class="extiw" title="commons:Chinese Characters">Chinese Characters</a></b></i></td>
</tr>
</table>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.skyren-art.com/art/index.php/en.html" class="external text" title="http://www.skyren-art.com/art/index.php/en.html" rel="nofollow">Art of Chinese Calligraphy</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.archchinese.com" class="external text" title="http://www.archchinese.com" rel="nofollow">Simplified Chinese Character Stroke Order and Dictionary</a>: Stroke order animations, dictionary and writing worksheets for every simplified Chinese character in the national standard character set.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.pinyin.info/readings/texts/visible/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.pinyin.info/readings/texts/visible/index.html" rel="nofollow">History of Chinese writing</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.chineseetymology.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.chineseetymology.org/" rel="nofollow">Chinese character etymologies</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.omniglot.com/writing/chinese_evolution.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.omniglot.com/writing/chinese_evolution.htm" rel="nofollow">Evolution of Chinese Characters</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.unicode.org/charts/unihan.html" class="external text" title="http://www.unicode.org/charts/unihan.html" rel="nofollow">Unihan Database</a>: Chinese, Japanese, and Korean references, readings, and meanings for all the Chinese and Chinese-derived characters in the <a href="/wiki/Unicode" title="Unicode">Unicode</a> character set</li>
<li><a href="http://www.clavisinica.com/character-test-applet.html" class="external text" title="http://www.clavisinica.com/character-test-applet.html" rel="nofollow">Chinese Character Test</a>: Online test helps you estimate how many Chinese characters you recognize.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.info.gov.hk/digital21/eng/structure/irg.html" class="external text" title="http://www.info.gov.hk/digital21/eng/structure/irg.html" rel="nofollow">IRG Page</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/~irg/" class="external text" title="http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/~irg/" rel="nofollow">IRG working documents</a>—many big size pdfs, some of them with details of CJK extensions</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mojikyo.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.mojikyo.org/" rel="nofollow">Welcome To Mojikyo Institute!</a>—big size downloadable <a href="/wiki/Mojikyo" title="Mojikyo">Mojikyo</a> program files</li>
<li><a href="http://www.vertical-sun.com/hanzi" class="external text" title="http://www.vertical-sun.com/hanzi" rel="nofollow">Hanzi Browser</a>: Chinese Character reference searchable by semantic/phonetic component</li>
<li><a href="http://stroke-order.learningweb.moe.edu.tw/index.jsp" class="external text" title="http://stroke-order.learningweb.moe.edu.tw/index.jsp" rel="nofollow">Stroke order for Chinese characters</a>: Official website for stroke order for Chinese characters</li>
<li><a href="http://www.learnmandarinonline.org/characters.html" class="external text" title="http://www.learnmandarinonline.org/characters.html" rel="nofollow">Chinese Characters</a>: Suggestions about How to Learn Chinese Character</li>
<li><a href="http://csymbol.com/words/index.html" class="external text" title="http://csymbol.com/words/index.html" rel="nofollow">English Words to Chinese Characters</a>: A large list of English words translated into Chinese characters</li>
</ul>
